{"title":"「NOIP2012」同余方程","time_limit":1000,"memory_limit":512,"tags":["模板"],"operation":{"submit":"https://syzoj.com/problem/639#submit_code","submissions":"https://syzoj.com/submissions?problem_id=639","statistics":"https://syzoj.com/problem/639/statistics/fastest","testdata":"https://syzoj.com/problem/639/testdata","discussion":"https://syzoj.com/discussion/problem/639"},"statement":[{"title":"题目描述","type":"description","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"求关于 $x$ 的同余方程 $ax \\equiv 1 \\pmod{b}$ 的最小正整数解。"},{"title":"输入格式","type":"input_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输入只有一行，包含两个正整数 $a, b$，用一个空格隔开。"},{"title":"输出格式","type":"output_format","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"输出只有一行，包含一个正整数 $x_0$，即最小正整数解。输入数据保证一定有解。"},{"title":"样例","type":"example","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"#### 样例输入 1\r\n```plainplain\r\n3 10\r\n```\r\n\r\n#### 样例输出 1\r\n```plainplain\r\n7\r\n```"},{"title":"数据范围与提示","type":"limit_and_hint","format":"markdown","require":["katex"],"content":"对于 40% 的数据，有 $2 \\leq b \\leq 1\\,000$；\r\n\r\n对于 60% 的数据，有 $2 \\leq b \\leq 50\\,000\\,000$；\r\n\r\n对于 100% 的数据，有 $2 \\leq a, b \\leq 2\\,000\\,000\\,000$。"}]}